definition.value: The group includes any type of Other tree nuts (exposure). The part consumed/analysed is by default unspecified. When relevant, information on the part consumed/analysed has to be reported with additional facet descriptors.

The group includes any type of Oilseeds as defined in EU pesticide regulation, including fruit seeds and vegetable seeds. The part consumed/analysed is not specified. When relevant, information on the part consumed/analysed has to be reported with additional facet descriptors. In case of data collections related to legislations, the default part consumed/analysed is the one defined in the applicable legislation.[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_edible_seeds] and [https://www.google.co.uk/search?tbm=isch&q=Oilseeds]
